<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, October 26 (Xinhua) -- South Korea became the first
Asian team to qualify for the France World Cup finals after Japan
and United Arab Emirates (UAE) tied 1-1 in an Asian zone group B
clash on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
South Korea is the 21st nation to claim a spot in next year's
finals.
</P>
<P>
