<HEADLINE> China's Industrial Sales Volume Grows Steadily (4) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 26 (Xinhua) -- China produced 4.29 trillion
yuan at current price in industrial sales volume during the first
eight months of this year, a year-on-year increase of 11.6 percent
</P>
<P>
(at constant price), the latest statistics from the State
Statistics Bureau said.
</P>
<P>
Of the total sales volume, the sector of light industry
contributed 1.89 trillion yuan, up 12.2 percent, while heavy
industry recorded 2.4 trillion yuan, a year-on-year growth of 11
percent.
</P>
<P>
The ratio of sales for industrial products was 95.1 percent,
rising by 0.7 percent. 
</P>
